--- src/lang-go.js ---
@sig 7ce14b2b
export parseGo(code,filename)→extractImports,stripStringsAndComments,structRegex.exec,getBody,code.substring,body.split|parse Go structs, interfaces, methods, and functions
extractImports(text)→text.replace,importBlockRegex.exec,block.split,line.match,imports.includes,imports.push|extract Go imports and package names
getBody(code,startIndex)→code.substring|extract block body using brace counting
extractCalls(body,packageNames)→callRegex.exec,keywords.includes,callName.includes,callName.split,packageNames.has,calls.includes|extract function calls ignoring Go keywords
PATTERNS: regex string extraction|brace counting for block scope
EDGE_CASES: ignores Go keywords|strips package prefix if alias matches